{"tid":662030,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[孤立無援] 有無一個人搬出黎住套房既巴打絲打？","createTime":"2018-05-12T05:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T06:36:57.000Z","uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bbea9ade1ce0aee1b09457735687a9a1296bfb5a","tid":662030,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"總算決定搬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget有限，諗住向九龍(深水埗、油尖旺最好)搵間$5000月租既套房<br />\n<br />\n見好多有廳靚裝修既都無電器傢俬，而包既就會細間d同舊，亦可能貴幾舊d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相比起自己買電器傢俬既錢，是咪都係頹頹地搵包埋既套房好d？<br />\n<br />\n自己一個睇樓有無咩要注意？（除左凶宅之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽講套房既水電煤好多都會比業主濫收，有無咩合約協議可以事前講定去提防濫收呢？<br />\n<br />\n問題比較多，爬左文但好多最後都不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有熱心巴絲可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a03f6a240f90dc93dfe44175a70f0f48f179ca","tid":662030,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"合租算吧LA"},{"pid":"bb995d784c27c05ad86ab91e02c616c4bd072998","tid":662030,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"油麻地有個共居<br />\n床位$3xxx<br />\n單人房$5xxx"},{"pid":"f5c8fef1fb02563f074368e7e4751f5b8b0c8121","tid":662030,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"真毒唔想同陌生人住，仲要夾生活習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb756c3e3004345a30797f88ba44cb153468bd05","tid":662030,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"搬左去一間細別墅，好撚細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955b5e0bcffeea132707b2f949cc6a7c845a0c93","tid":662030,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:06:55.000Z